      "writtenOn": "2016-09-30T02:20:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do we need to Update first?\n\nDo we need to worry about ordering with JobFinished? E.g.\n1. goroutine 1 calls sendHeartbeats, gets Job A from UnfinishedJobs\n2. goroutine 2 calls TaskScheduler.updateUnfinishedJobs, gets Job A from UnfinishedJobs\n3. goroutine 2 calls JobFinished on Job A; we tell Build Bucket that the job is finished\n4. goroutine 1 sends a heartbeat for Job A; Build Bucket returns an error\n5. goroutine 1 calls localCancelJobs and gets ErrConcurrentUpdate",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 109,
        "startChar": 24,
        "endLine": 109,
        "endChar": 49
      },
      "revId": "6e4273af9d602d7e1a29efd1a87d8dcdb030c970",
