      "writtenOn": "2016-09-30T18:47:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Added the update. I agree that this could be an issue. Two solutions I can think of right now:\n1. Just add a mutex for sendHeartbeats and JobFinished. It\u0027s dumb and would be slow but would work.\n2. Add a \"finished\" queue to TryJobIntegrator and send the actual job finished notifications *during* sendHeartbeats, instead of the heartbeat itself.",
      "parentUuid": "a566efce_8e326b5c",
      "revId": "6e4273af9d602d7e1a29efd1a87d8dcdb030c970",
